"title": "2324: Jesus Christ, as Saviour",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2324",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's work of salvation is accomplished supremely through the cross and resurrection of Jesus Christ. Through faith, the believer is able to share in all the saving benefits won by Jesus Christ through his obedience to God.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the Saviour</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is called Saviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:4\">TIT 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:11\">LUK 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:6\">TIT 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1\">2PE 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:2\">2PE 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the promised Saviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:23\">ACT 13:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:69-Luke1:75\">LUK 1:69–1:75</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:28-Luke2:30\">LUK 2:28–2:30</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's purpose is to save</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:10\">LUK 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">MAT 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's qualities as Saviour</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the unique Saviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:68-John6:69\">JHN 6:68–6:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:9\">JHN 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:42-Acts10:43\">ACT 10:42–10:43</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the complete Saviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:19-Col1:20\">COL 1:19–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:9\">HEB 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:26-Heb9:28\">HEB 9:26–9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:9\">1JN 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is the Saviour of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:42\">JHN 4:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:30-Luke2:32\">LUK 2:30–2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5-1Tim2:6\">1TI 2:5–2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:10\">1TI 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:14\">1JN 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ saves through his grace</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:11\">ACT 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:24\">ROM 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23-Eph5:27\">EPH 5:23–5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:5\">TIT 3:4–3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ saves by his mighty acts</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves by his death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:18–1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:28\">MAT 20:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:45\">MRK 10:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:45-Luke24:47\">LUK 24:45–24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:29\">JHN 1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:36\">JHN 1:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:15\">JHN 10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:17-John10:18\">JHN 10:17–10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:10\">REV 7:10</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves by his resurrection life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:21\">1PE 3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:10\">ROM 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves by his coming again</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:20\">PHP 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:13\">TIT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves by defeating Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:31\">JHN 13:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:11\">JHN 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10-Rev2:11\">REV 2:10–2:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ saves from all forms of evil</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves from physical danger</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:25-Matt8:26\">MAT 8:25–8:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:38-Mark4:39\">MRK 4:38–4:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:24-Luke8:25\">LUK 8:24–8:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:17\">ACT 26:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves from the power of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:7\">1JN 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31\">ACT 5:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:25–3:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:18-Rom5:19\">ROM 5:18–5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:6-Rom6:7\">ROM 6:6–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:4\">GAL 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5-Rev1:6\">REV 1:5–1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves from the condemnation of law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38-Acts13:39\">ACT 13:38–13:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1-Rom8:4\">ROM 8:1–8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:4–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:15\">EPH 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves from God's wrath</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:10\">1TH 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:9\">ROM 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:9\">1TH 5:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:17-Rev11:18\">REV 11:17–11:18</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves from the power of death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:55-1Cor15:57\">1CO 15:55–15:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:15\">HEB 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:6\">REV 20:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves from Satan's power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:18\">ACT 26:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:18-Luke10:19\">LUK 10:18–10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:13\">COL 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ saves to bring people to God</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves for eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:40\">JHN 6:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:16\">JHN 3:14–3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24-John5:25\">JHN 5:24–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ saves so that people may live for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9\">1JN 4:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:8-Rom6:11\">ROM 6:8–6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:21-Rom7:25\">ROM 7:21–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14-Heb9:15\">HEB 9:14–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:5-1John3:6\">1JN 3:5–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:18\">1JN 5:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's salvation is received through faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:30-Acts16:31\">ACT 16:30–16:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:21\">ACT 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:13\">ROM 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:32\">JOL 2:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16\">ROM 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9\">ROM 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:15\">2TI 3:15</a></p>",
